      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "② 预处理（每 view，共 241×4 张）\nimg → crop[162:737, 0:1100] → (575, 1100, 3)\nB-mode = [:, :590] → (575, 590, 3) ｜ ULM = [:, 590:] → (575, 510, 3)，ULM 右侧 10% 置零\npad_sq 补零成方形 → resize(224,224) → BGR→RGB, /255 → ImageNet normalize → (3, 224, 224)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
