      "text": "⑤ 双路投影（VascMambaHybrid.forward, d_model=32）\nbmode_proj = Linear(512→32)+LayerNorm+GELU：(B,4,512) → (B,4,32)\nulm_proj   = Linear(512→32)+LayerNorm+GELU：(B,4,512) → (B,4,32)",
