    {
      "type": "text", "id": "txtF", "x": 140, "y": 614, "width": 860, "height": 84, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "seed": 18, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 18, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "⑥ Vessel-guided 排序 + 序列拼装\nu_tokens 按 density 降序 gather 重排：(B,4,32)（主流程中 4 个 density 相同 → 恒等排序）\n交错拼接 [B1,U1,B2,U2,B3,U3,B4,U4] → tokens (B, 8, 32)\n+ mod_emb(1,2,32)[0,1,0,1,0,1,0,1]（偶=B-mode, 奇=ULM） + pos_emb(1,8,32) → (B, 8, 32)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 76,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⑥ Vessel-guided 排序 + 序列拼装\nu_tokens 按 density 降序 gather 重排：(B,4,32)（主流程中 4 个 density 相同 → 恒等排序）\n交错拼接 [B1,U1,B2,U2,B3,U3,B4,U4] → tokens (B, 8, 32)\n+ mod_emb(1,2,32)[0,1,0,1,0,1,0,1]（偶=B-mode, 奇=ULM） + pos_emb(1,8,32) → (B, 8, 32)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {"type": "arrow", "id": "arrF", "x": 570, "y": 706, "width": 0, "height": 20, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 2}, "seed": 19, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 19, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "points": [[0, 0], [0, 20]], "lastCommittedPoint": null, "startBinding": null, "endBinding": null, "startArrowhead": null, "endArrowhead": "arrow"},

    {
      "type": "rectangle", "id": "boxG", "x": 120, "y": 726, "width": 900, "height": 210, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00", "backgroundColor": "#ffec99", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "seed": 20, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 20, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "txtG", "x": 140, "y": 734, "width": 860, "height": 194, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "seed": 21, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 21, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "⑦ MambaBlock ×1（d_model=32, d_state=4, d_conv=2, expand=2, d_inner=64）\nx = x + SSM(LN(x))；x = x + FFN(LN(x))，FFN: 32→128→GELU→32\nSelectiveSSM 内部：\n  in_proj: (B,8,32)→(B,8,128) → chunk → x_in, z 各 (B,8,64)\n  depthwise Conv1d(64, k=2, pad=1) → 截断 :8 → SiLU：(B,8,64)\n  x_proj: (B,8,64)→(B,8,9) → B_ssm (B,8,4), C_ssm (B,8,4)；dt = softplus(dt_proj)：(B,8,1)\n  A = −exp(A_log)：(4,)；Ā = exp(dt·A)：(B,8,1,4)；B̄ = dt·B·x：(B,8,64,4)\n  逐步扫描 t=0..7：h(B,64,4) = Ā_t·h + B̄_t；y_t = (h·C_t).sum(-1) → (B,64)\n  y_scan (B,8,64) ⊙ SiLU(z) → out_proj(64→32) → (B,8,32)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 187,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⑦ MambaBlock ×1（d_model=32, d_state=4, d_conv=2, expand=2, d_inner=64）\nx = x + SSM(LN(x))；x = x + FFN(LN(x))，FFN: 32→128→GELU→32\nSelectiveSSM 内部：\n  in_proj: (B,8,32)→(B,8,128) → chunk → x_in, z 各 (B,8,64)\n  depthwise Conv1d(64, k=2, pad=1) → 截断 :8 → SiLU：(B,8,64)\n  x_proj: (B,8,64)→(B,8,9) → B_ssm (B,8,4), C_ssm (B,8,4)；dt = softplus(dt_proj)：(B,8,1)\n  A = −exp(A_log)：(4,)；Ā = exp(dt·A)：(B,8,1,4)；B̄ = dt·B·x：(B,8,64,4)\n  逐步扫描 t=0..7：h(B,64,4) = Ā_t·h + B̄_t；y_t = (h·C_t).sum(-1) → (B,64)\n  y_scan (B,8,64) ⊙ SiLU(z) → out_proj(64→32) → (B,8,32)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

