      "originalText": "⑧ 池化 + 分类头\nmean over sequence dim：(B,8,32) → (B,32)\nhead = LayerNorm → Linear(32→32)+GELU+Dropout(0.3) → Linear(32→2) → logits (B, 2)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {"type": "arrow", "id": "arrH", "x": 570, "y": 1036, "width": 0, "height": 20, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 2}, "seed": 25, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 25, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "points": [[0, 0], [0, 20]], "lastCommittedPoint": null, "startBinding": null, "endBinding": null, "startArrowhead": null, "endArrowhead": "arrow"},

    {
      "type": "rectangle", "id": "boxI", "x": 120, "y": 1056, "width": 900, "height": 118, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "seed": 26, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 26, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "txtI", "x": 140, "y": 1064, "width": 860, "height": 102, "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "seed": 27, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 27, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "⑨ 训练 / 推理\nloss = CrossEntropyLoss(weight=[3.0, 1.0])（恶性:良性 = 3:1 类权重）\nAdamW(lr=5e-4, wd=5e-3) + CosineAnnealingLR + grad clip 2.0；100 epochs，early stop patience=20\n验证：softmax[:,1] → 阈值搜索 [0.05, 0.95) step 0.02 取 F1 最大 → acc/auc/recall/f1\n5-fold StratifiedKFold(seed=42) 取均值 → ACC 87.98%（baseline：BC-SVM 85.48%）",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 96,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⑨ 训练 / 推理\nloss = CrossEntropyLoss(weight=[3.0, 1.0])（恶性:良性 = 3:1 类权重）\nAdamW(lr=5e-4, wd=5e-3) + CosineAnnealingLR + grad clip 2.0；100 epochs，early stop patience=20\n验证：softmax[:,1] → 阈值搜索 [0.05, 0.95) step 0.02 取 F1 最大 → acc/auc/recall/f1\n5-fold StratifiedKFold(seed=42) 取均值 → ACC 87.98%（baseline：BC-SVM 85.48%）",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

